                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div><!--/#home-page-->

            <div id="about-page" class="item">
                <div class="container">

                    <div class="vertical-middle">
                        <div class="vertical-middle-inner">

                            <div class="text-center">
                                <h2 class="page-header">About Us</h2>
                            </div>

                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-sm-4">
                                    <div class="box">
                                        <h3>Our Team</h3>
                                        <p>We are four aspiring developers currently completing a Web Programming course at Tufts University</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-4">
                                    <div class="box">
                                        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                                        <p>Using your starred music playlist, we recommend various local unknown artists which you might enjoy. </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-4">
                                    <div class="box">
                                        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
                                        <p>There are so many talented artists and performers that go unnoticed due to lack of publicity. We hope to link small, talented artists with users </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>              
            </div><!--/#about-page-->

             <div id="features-page" class="item">
                <div class="container">

                    <div class="vertical-middle">
                        <div class="vertical-middle-inner">

                            <div class="text-center">
                                <h2 class="page-header">Our Features</h2>
                            </div>

                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-sm-4">
                                    <div class="box">
                                        <h3>Local Events </h3>
                                        <p>See a full list of upcoming performances in venues close to you</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-4">
                                    <div class="box">
                                        <h3>Seamless Integration with your Google Account</h3>
                                        <p>Get directions to venues, add events to your calendars with just one click. </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-4">
                                    <div class="box">
                                        <h3> Music Preference Analytics</h3>
                                        <p>View a breakdown of the genres most frequently found on you Starred playlist. </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>              
            </div><!--/#features-page-->

            <div id="developer-page" class="item">
                <div class="container">

                    <div class="vertical-middle">
                        <div class="vertical-middle-inner">

                            <div class="text-center">
                                <h2 class="page-header">Our Developers</h2>
                            </div>

                            <div class="row">

                                <div class="col-sm-3">
                                    <div class="overlay-container">
                                        <img class="img-responsive" src="images/akshi.jpg" alt="">
                                        <div class="overlay">
                                            <div class="vertical-middle">
                                                <div class="vertical-middle-inner">
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-3">
                                    <div class="overlay-container">
                                        <img class="img-responsive" src="images/scott.jpg" alt="">
                                        <div class="overlay">
                                            <div class="vertical-middle">
                                                <div class="vertical-middle-inner">
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                 <div class="col-sm-3">
                                    <div class="overlay-container">
                                        <img class="img-responsive" src="images/sam.jpg" alt="">
                                        <div class="overlay">
                                            <div class="vertical-middle">
                                                <div class="vertical-middle-inner">
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                  </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-3">
                                    <div class="overlay-container">
                                        <img class="img-responsive" src="images/jack.jpg" alt="">
                                        <div class="overlay">
                                            <div class="vertical-middle">
                                                <div class="vertical-middle-inner">
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                 </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>                
            </div><!--/#developer-page-->

            <div id="contact-page" class="item">
                <div class="container">

                    <div class="vertical-middle">
                        <div class="vertical-middle-inner">

                            <div class="text-center">
                                <h2 class="page-header">Contact Us</h2>
                            </div>

                            <form class="form-horizontal" id="contact-form" role="form">
                                <div class="form-group form-status">
                                    <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-6">
                                        <div class="form-status-content">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-6">
                                        <input type="text" name="name" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Name" required="required">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-6">
                                        <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Email" required="required">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-6">
                                        <input type="text" name="subject" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Subject" required="required">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8">
                                        <textarea name="message" rows="6" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Message" required="required"></textarea>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8">
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-transparent" onsubmit = "homeformsubmit()">Send Message</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </form>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>                
            </div><!--/#contact-page-->
        </div><!--/.carousel-inner-->
